title: 275: Rhett's Spiritual Deconstruction - One Year Later | Ear Biscuits Ep.275
description:
It's been a full year (and what a year it has been) since the guys have unveiled their spiritual deconstruction stories. Listen to Rhett's one year follow-up as he discusses how he processed the year that was 2020 post-deconstruction and where he's at now spiritually in this episode of Ear Biscuits!
